  Destructor had been working on the blasted machine for quite some time. He 
suddenly shouted in sucess..."We have done it. Now I wish you to keep testing 
this. Me and Kit Kat will test the final process in the morning. I dont want 
her to be worried by this in her weakened stage." He walked into the 
lab...."Kit Kat the replicators are in thier final cycle. I want you to get 
some rest so we may test it in the morning with all our wits about us. " He 
took her hand.."I have known you for a short time and yet you make me worry 
by being so stubborn. Please , let me take you to your quaters for some 
sleep."
